
This repository contains the sets of scripts used by Usint (User Interface).

Check_approved_obs  --- Check updates_table.list and send out email
Chkupdata           --- cgi script lets USINT to inspect changes made on the parameters of observation
Express_signoff     --- cgi script lets USINT to approve multiple observation at the same time
Find_mishatch       --- check update_table.list and check whether a phantom entry is created in the list
Find_planned_roll   --- extract planned roll agnles
Find_schedule_obs   --- inds which observations is MP scheduled
Go_form             --- Updating letter generator for new AO
Html_pages          --- Save html pages used by USINT
Input_new_contact   --- cgi script lets USINT to update contact information
Make_access_list    --- makes a list of users who can access to the observations
Ocat                --- functions that create Ocat Data Page and related interactive web pages using python django
Ocatdata_page       --- cgi script let USINT to update observational parameters
Orupdate            --- cgi script let all requested updates which have either not been verified or have been verified in the last 24 hours
POC_notification    --- sends out POC duty notification
POC_OBSIDS          --- cgi script lists approved TOO/DDT and thier POC/observations handled by a given POC
Remove_submission   --- cgi script lets USINT user to remove an accidental submission
Schedule_page       --- cgi script lets USINT to choose when they want to assume POC responsibility
                        and a perl script creates a html page from a given schedule
Sign_off_request    --- sends out signoff requests to user
SOT_observation     --- A ksh script to run sot_data.sql and the sql script obtains specified column values from database from all data
Split_check         --- check whether a newly added obsid is a split observation, and send notify to POC.
This_week_POC       --- finds who is this week's POC and update /home/mta/TOO-POC
TOO_Obs             --- Check TOO/DDT observations and update related information
Updated_targets     --- cgi script lists all targets which have been verified as updated
Update_passowrd     --- Check whether any of the users listed changed her/his passwoard and update the password list
Update_Targets      --- cgi script lists all targets which have been verified as updated
